## Proposed Changes

### Auth — Registration Feature

#### [NEW] [register.blade.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/job-board/resources/views/auth/register.blade.php)
- Sign-up form with **Name**, **Email**, **Password**, and **Confirm Password** fields.
- Links to the login page ("Already have an account? Sign in").
- Uses existing `<x-layout>`, `<x-card>`, `<x-text-input>`, `<x-button>` components.

#### [MODIFY] [create.blade.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/job-board/resources/views/auth/create.blade.php)
- Add a link at the bottom: "Don't have an account? Sign up" pointing to the register route.

#### [MODIFY] [AuthController.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/job-board/app/Http/Controllers/AuthController.php)
- Add `showRegister()` — returns the `auth.register` view.
- Add `register(Request $request)` — validates input, creates the user, logs them in, and redirects to `/`.

